## 🎯 Executive Summary

The **AR Token Capture System** enables users to discover and collect TRV tokens through **GPS-based Augmented Reality (AR)** experiences while exploring the real world. Users can physically move to locations, view tokens in AR, capture them, and meet new people in the process. This creates an immersive, gamified experience that bridges the digital and physical worlds while driving community growth and user engagement.

### Core Value Proposition
- 🗺️ **GPS-Based Discovery**: Find TRV tokens in real-world locations
- 📱 **AR Capture**: Collect tokens through immersive AR experiences
- 👥 **Social Discovery**: Meet new people while collecting tokens
- 🎁 **Onboarding Bonuses**: Bonus rewards for connecting with new users
- 🌍 **Global Exploration**: Tokens distributed worldwide for community building
- 🎮 **Gamified Experience**: Make token collection fun and engaging

